**Overall Meaning:**

The supreme Brahman, devoid of qualities and form, becomes the Supreme Lord with qualities and form for the devotees, due to the effect of their cool devotion, just as ice, due to coldness, forms from water. He, the Supreme Lord, is the indweller of the entire universe. 
